NMDCX
------
NMDC is Neo Modus' Direct Connect Protocol. Full protocol at http://nmdc.sourceforge.net.

Usage
-----
Create a python file like

+------------------------------------------+
|                                          |
|  from PlainTalk import *                 |
|  pt = PlainTalk(HUB, USERNAME, PASSWORD) |
|  pt.talk()                               |
|                                          |
+------------------------------------------+
   

To do
